[[File:en/Manual/OpenttdLogo.png|left|150px]] '''OpenTTD''' is an [https://www.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open_Source open source] clone of the Microprose game [https://www.wikipedia.org/wiki/Transport_Tycoon Transport Tycoon Deluxe (TTD)]. 

You play the role of president of a start-up transport company in 1950, building railway, road, air and maritime transportation systems for commodities and people. The goal of the game is to outsmart your competition and become the game's highest-ranking transport company by the year 2050.

OpenTTD runs on Mac OS X, Linux, Unix, BeOS, OS/2, Windows and a few other [[en/Archive/Compilation and Ports/Operating system|platforms]].
