==Features==
While the game is modelled after the original by [http://www.chrissawyer.com/info.htm Chris Sawyer], OpenTTD has many additional features that enhance gameplay dramatically. OpenTTD has customizable game graphics, and work is underway to replace TTD's graphics completely. Many features were inspired by [http://www.ttdpatch.net/ TTDPatch], a popular enhancement for TTD, while other features are original. OpenTTD is far more customisable than Transport Tycoon deluxe through the use of [[en/Community/Patches/Patches]] and [[en/Manual/NewGRF|custom graphics]].

OpenTTD is also compatible with many more [[en/Archive/Compilation and Ports/Operating system]]s.

